      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, combine your<strong> gochujang paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> in a bowl with<strong> half </strong>your <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>agave</strong> and <strong>sriracha </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy sauce</strong></p><p>Trim, then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678299375122-x200.jpg",
