      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>tofu</strong> into cubes, then add to a bowl with<strong> </strong>the<strong> remaining tamari soy sauce </strong>and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]<strong> </span>cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Once fully coated, add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to the bowl and mix it all together until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
