      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>(enough to cover the whole base of the pan) over a high heat</p><p>Once the pan is very hot, add the <strong>coated tofu</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side until golden and crispy – this is your<strong> crispy tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
