    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, combine 1/2 tbsp per person of the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>spicy sauce </strong>and<strong> mayo</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>carrot, mooli & pink cabbage slaw mix </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> spicy slaw</strong></p>",
