    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is golden and crispy, transfer to kitchen paper and carefully pour away the oil (reserve the pan!)</p><p>Tip: You can use this oil again in another recipe!</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and add the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>spicy sauce</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, add the<strong> crispy tofu </strong>with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy Korean-style popcorn tofu</strong></p>",
