    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy Korean-style popcorn tofu </strong>with the <strong>sushi rice</strong> and <strong>spicy slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
